text: "Jurassic Park" is a song by "Weird Al" Yankovic. It is a parody of "MacArthur Park" by Jimmy Webb (as performed by Richard Harris). It is a humorous retelling of the plot in the novel and movie Jurassic Park. It is on the album Alaplooza released in 1993. Category:"Weird Al" Yankovic songs Category:Parodies Category:1993 songs
title: Jurassic Park (song)
